              <Comment>NTDT or non severe type of Thalassemia . Variant was found in a 6 year old girl suffering with anemia. coinherited with another deletion variant in HBD-HBB genomic region. Base line hemoglobin level of 10.7 g/dl. Due to the coinheritance of both allele deletion in HBB and HBD genomic region HbA2 is 0 % and maximum hemoglobin is HbF 96.5%.</Comment>
